<l>ikaletir cāyntoḻuka vallārai yārē </l>
<l>mikalūkkun taṉmai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who indeed would think of conquering those who naturally shrink back from hatred ?</l>
